---
import productSteelBuilding from "../assets/product-steel-building.webp";
import productBetweenTheTrails from "../assets/product-between-the-trails.jpg";
import productCampfireReady from "../assets/product-campfire-ready.jpg";
import productHotFood from "../assets/product-hot-food.jpg";
import productAlcoholBeerTobacco from "../assets/product-alcohol.png";
---

<section id="products">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="product-category" id="steel-buildings">
			<a class="product-category-header" href="/steel-buildings">
				<div class="product-image">
					<img src={productSteelBuilding.src} alt="Steel Building" />
				</div>
				<h2>Steel Buildings</h2>
				<h3>RV Carports &mdash; Shield Your Home on Wheels</h3>
			</a>

			<div class="product-card">
				<p>
					Your RV is an investment—protect it like one. Our tall,
					<strong>open-sided carports</strong> are specially designed to accommodate
					<strong>RVs, motorhomes, and travel trailers</strong>. Choose extra height, add side
					panels for better weather protection, or fully enclose it for long-term storage.
				</p>
				<p>
					<a href="/steel-buildings" class="btn"
						>Get a free quote and see how easy it is to get covered <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span
						></a
					>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="product-category" id="between-the-trails">
			<a class="product-category-header" href="location.html">
				<div class="product-image">
					<img src={productBetweenTheTrails.src} alt="Between the Trails" />
				</div>
				<h2>Between the Trails &amp; Home</h2>
				<h3>Headed in or heading out &mdash; we're always on the way</h3>
			</a>
			<div class="product-card">
				<p>
					Tucked away in the heart of Missouri's scenic countryside, our little country store at <strong
						>Woodland Lakes in Sullivan, MO</strong
					> is more than just a pit stop— it's a friendly place where locals, campers, and park-goers
					all come together. Conveniently accessible both from inside the Woodland Lakes community and
					from Mine Road outside, we're a perfect stop before or after your next adventure.
				</p>
				<p>
					<a href="location.html" class="btn"
						>All the essentials, right where you need 'em <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a
					>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="product-category" id="campfire-ready">
			<a class="product-category-header" href="location.html">
				<div class="product-image">
					<img src={productCampfireReady.src} alt="Campfire Ready" />
				</div>
				<h2>Campfire Ready in One Stop</h2>
				<h3>Be prepared for an evening under the stars</h3>
			</a>

			<div class="product-card">
				<p>
					We're proud to serve folks heading out to explore <strong>Meramec State Park</strong>, <strong
						>Onondaga Cave State Park</strong
					>, or the sprawling <strong>Mark Twain National Forest</strong>—some of Missouri's finest
					destinations for hiking, camping, floating, and good old-fashioned outdoor fun. Whether
					you're loading up for a weekend under the stars or just wrapping up a long day on the
					trails, we've got what you need.
				</p>
				<p>
					<a href="location.html" class="btn"
						>Don't drive to town &mdash; we've got what you need right here <span class="arrow"
							>&rarr;</span
						></a
					>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="product-category" id="fresh-hot-food">
			<a class="product-category-header" href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1EU4qrfmiK/">
				<div class="product-image">
					<img src={productHotFood.src} alt="Fresh Hot Food" />
				</div>
				<h2>Fresh Hot Food</h2>
				<h3>Meals that Hit the Spot & Snacks for the Road</h3>
			</a>

			<div class="product-card">
				<p>
					Grab a hot meal from our kitchen—<strong>burgers</strong>, <strong>breakfast</strong>, <strong
						>pizza</strong
					>, <strong>shakes</strong>, and more—or stock up on cold beer, spirits, and tobacco
					products to help you unwind. We also carry groceries, camping gear, ice, and snacks, so
					you won't have to run all over town. And if you're planning ahead for your property or
					campsite, check out our lineup of <strong>steel buildings</strong> and
					<strong></strong>carports
				</p>, custom-built and ready for delivery.
			</div>
			<p>
				<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1EU4qrfmiK/" target="_blank" class="btn"
					>Daily specials and hot meals &mdash; you won't leave disappointed <span class="arrow"
						>&rarr;</span
					></a
				>
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="product-category" id="alcohol-beer-tobacco">
		<a class="product-category-header" href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1EU4qrfmiK/">
			<div class="product-image">
				<img src={productAlcoholBeerTobacco.src} alt="Alcohol, Beer, & Tobacco" />
			</div>
			<h2>Alcohol, Beer, & Tobacco</h2>
			<h3>Mixers & More for the Perfect Pour</h3>
		</a>

		<div class="product-card">
			<p>
				From <strong>hot food</strong> and <strong>cold drinks</strong> to sturdy buildings and trail-ready
				supplies, you'll always find a <em>Lil Bit of Something</em> here. Stop by, say hello, and let
				us help you get set for whatever's next.
			</p>
			<p>
				<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1EU4qrfmiK/" target="_blank" class="btn"
					>Call ahead or stop by; we'll have it hot and ready <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a
				>
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

